api_list.name: dnsLookup
api_list.description: Retrieve all the DNS records of any domain with DNS Lookup.

required_parameters.name: domain
required_parameters.description: Domain you want to retrieve the records for.

api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://the-domain-tool.p.rapidapi.com/dnslookup/example.com"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "the-domain-tool.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
api_list.convert_code:
import requests

url = "https://the-domain-tool.p.rapidapi.com/dnslookup/{domain}"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "the-domain-tool.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
